Q1 - Write a controlled form in React with two fields: patientName and email .Use useState to track each Field. 
     On submit , log the form valuse to the console and reset both fields to empty strings. 
     Add a basic check that prevents submission if either field is empty.


Q2 - Set up React Router with three routes: / (Home page), / about , and /contact Add a navigation bar with links  to all three pages. 
Each page should render a simple heading indentifying itself.
